	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I didn't enjoy school at all. Work is okay. For some reason nearly 100% of the joy I get out of life is all in hobbies. At least I don't hate my job and there's little pressure to work more than 40h a week, so that's nice. I have a lot of peers for whom it often is 60h or more a week. I couldn't live that way, I'd rather make less money. Nearly all my spare time is making games or music.

		

